Package: mirBottleneck
Title: miRNA Bottleneck Scoring for Cancer Survival Prediction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mark Barsoum", "Markarian",
    email = "mb.markarian@aub.edu.lb",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Identifies miRNAs acting as transcriptome stabilizers in cancer
    using two complementary scores: variance suppression (how much a miRNA
    reduces target gene variance) and coherence induction (how much a miRNA
    coordinates target gene programs). Classifies miRNAs into silencer,
    conductor, dual, and weak categories. Computes a composite patient-level
    bottleneck index and evaluates its association with overall survival.
